{
  "texts": [
    "The students viewed the 3D versions of the organs of the digestive system. 4.",
    "Students completed the activities listed below: o Activity 1: Quiz o Activity 2: Labeling anatomical structures o Activity 3: Puzzle o Activity 4: The journey of food Active Learning Space (LMS) 1.",
    "Students explained the purpose, function and digestion process of the digestive system in their own words (Revision part) 2.",
    "They answered the quiz about the digestive system process prepared in kahoot (Revision part). 3.",
    "They participated in group discussion about the functions of organs."
  ]
